Enum AudioVideoCommandNumber

java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<AudioVideoCommandNumber>
public enum AudioVideoCommandNumber
extends java.lang.Enum<AudioVideoCommandNumber>

Defines command numbers to use for Audio and Video control. Used in the AudioCommand and VideoCommand events, as well as the updateAudioCommandStatus and updateVideoCommandStatus commands.
